  <title>Fonts</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Fonts</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">If the pdf document don&apos;t show the correct written characters of one language. Especially Tamil or other arabic, asian languages.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">This is the way to do it.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">We have to install one font, for this follow the following steps:</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">1. Open the Windows Explorer and go in the folder C:\Bibletool\font</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="Windows font01.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="50.00%" width="462" height="186" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">2. The relevant files here are only far.ttf and fab.ttf:</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="Windows font02.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="50.00%" width="318" height="81" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="page-break-before:always;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">3. For each file do this:</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">3.1 Open with a doubleclick the file far.ttf or fab.ttf</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="Windows font03.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="40.00%" width="572" height="300" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">3.2 Click on Install</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="Windows font04.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="60.00%" width="154" height="83" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">4. After you installed both the far.ttf and fab.ttf you can ran the Bibletool again and it should show the font correctly</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="page-break-before:always;"></para>
  </body>
